snippet.title: Overpower Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Store: http://store.steampowered.com/app/440280/
Humble Widget: http://www.overpowergame.com/purchase/

Overpower is a 3rd person fantasy shooter game. Inspired by the pick-up and play nature of a shooter combined with epic RPG style class based PvP. Overpower puts a skill based twist on traditional arena games, putting players immediately into the action. Low cooldowns and 
split second decision making allows players to Overpower their opponents no matter who or what they're up against!
